name: Touching Universe
description:
I had come a long way, And in this spiritual journey, I was confronted with new dimensions of myself
I had the last stop after which I would return home.
I reached Sazak mountains...
Pastures full of flowers, which reached a dreamy beach at the foot of the mountains, And the mountains that took me to a cave in a crazy way...They created a dreamy and transcendental image for me.
What I had to touch I touched on this journey
